Arguments heard as to bail. Court granted defense motion and ordered cash bail adjusted down to $5,000.00 with turnover to Justice Point monitoring with the following conditions:
-24 Hour curfew. Defendant will be allowed to leave his home for court appearances, emergency medical issues, and attorney meetings. Meetings with his attorney must be verified in advance by Justice Point.
-No one may reside in the defendant's home who is under the age of 21 years;
-No contact with the victims ANS, HRS, and SR;
-Defendant may not have contact with the victims over the phone or through a third party.
